The Wrong Box (1966) - Michael Caine - Peter Sellers - DVD XviD
Comedy

Cast: Michael Caine, Peter Cook, Dudley Moore, Nanette Newman, John Mills, Ralph Richardson, Peter Sellers

Directed by: Bryan Forbes

A tontine is established for a dozen children, a tontine being a kind of bet - insurance, money is put in for each to grow with interest and the last survivor is to get the lot. We watch the group dwindle until only two brothers are left. One brother is watched by his nephews who will keep him alive at all costs, the other lives in ill health and poverty as the only support of his fairly stupid grandson. Statues and bodies are switched, in the wrong boxes until everyone is sure someone has died. Now if they can only make it seem as if the other brother died first, hundreds of thousands of pounds will be theirs.
